{"id": "1320018455256367114", "channel_id": "1320018455256367114", "type": 0, "author_id": "1302298693369856000", "author_name": "flim_of_life_burst", "author_bot": false, "content": "▼▼▼▼：生日快樂。你似乎不高興？\n    \n索瓦爾格：你知道這種程度的進食對我來說毫無意義。\n    \n▼▼▼▼：但你喜歡人類的食物——尤其是柔軟而甜蜜的蛋糕。況且，這是她為你準備的晚餐。\n    \n索瓦爾格：“母親”已經放棄我了。\n    \n索瓦爾格：……至少你還在。\n    \n▼▼▼▼：永遠不要指望其他人。\n    \n▼▼▼▼：你有著暴戾的血液，但並沒有流露過這種天性，這很奇怪。\n    \n▼▼▼▼：我仍然相信你的野心只是暫時蟄伏。\n    \n▼▼▼▼：呵呵……有朝一日你也會成為高塔上的暴君麼？我很期待那一天的到來，並且樂意親自為你加冕。", "timestamp": "2024-12-21T13:22:04.490000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "1nekodrool", "emoji_id": "1206774407562006600", "count": 17}], "attachments": [{"id": "1320018455688249435", "filename": "0a00d3734b5b6905884d2440ee57342e.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 501015, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1320018455256367114/1320018455688249435/0a00d3734b5b6905884d2440ee57342e.jpg?ex=69fb407c&is=69f9eefc&hm=ef3983b2bccca193ad6bc878368a8be422b5ba54cda851ae0ad8b941fb6f630a&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1320018455256367114", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "生日快樂，索瓦爾格/Happy Birthday to Solvarg Vol. 2", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "is_thread_starter": true}
